# E2E tests

If a test is testing for 0-downtime operations, no transient failures are allowed for that test.
Do not twist it around.

Use ginkgo to run individual E2E tests or "make test-e2e" to run the whole test suite.

E2E tests are not deploying the operator in the cluster but they run it in-process.

Instead of waiting for 120 seconds to verify some test behaviour, prefer using a small script that checks every few seconds in a loop and exits when test is done running.
